Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please do not go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't come to examination anymore..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:30.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:31.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:34.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:36.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:40.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but like this, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..\Nhe might have crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:47.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you finished with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This means he is in love, right?\Nwith Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Counter-transference.. What just happened\Nmight be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:04.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though he had the habit of saying\Nhe'd return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This time is for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It sounds real, like he usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean is it treatment? Is it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder which one is?\N{\3c&H573235&}I'm the one asking the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By the time when the first symptoms appear\Nyou can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:22.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Mizushima\Nhave never spoken clear to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:25.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:28.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,might intend to quit as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I guess that's how strong\Nhis resolution is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is this, what Akira-san\Nwanted to do the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't?\N{\3c&H573235&}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:06.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. I really like this.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It really looks well on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:24.64,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Even though I didn't expect her condition\Nto have this sudden improvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.14,Self tought,,0,0,0,,now, it looks like I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:31.53,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Because, at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:35.03,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Akira-san and Yumeno-san\Nseem to have become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come, come come..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, running again?\NAre you running again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:53.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, I'll do it!\NSince I'm the one who can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:57.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's kicking the wall.\NAfter a long time, the tic disorder seems to have reappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I'll say 'do it', you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Listen you guys,\Nthe acquisition will be an absolute success, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can take the whole country,\NI have what it takes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think you're right.\N{\3c&H573235&}You fool, don't sympathize with such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There was a phone call this morning, from Minister Ike,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it was about...\N{\3c&H573235&}What? Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:24.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The acquisition issue is not longer possible, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll be my horse.\N{\3c&H573235&}eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm saying you'll be my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wa..wait..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait,\Nplease calm down, Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa, lead my horse Miyagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:41.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious? To the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I eat such a delicious omurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Which omurice do you like the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mm..that one, I prefer the jumble one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:01.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Me too, let's prepare them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:20.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait! Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait ~! \N{\3c&H573235&}Aa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah my stomach aches!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:29.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:35.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Ruriko-san~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:40.54,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:44.56,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.13,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.53,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:05:00.04,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:04.55,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.4,52.2)}The last time~! \NDr. Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:36.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I come tomorrow as well?\N{\3c&H573235&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm leaving for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Or else, Okiya's mom will get worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll take you home.\N{\3c&H573235&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:51.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if we're not together all the time..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a copy of the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:18.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a phone call from Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:29.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry I made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aizawa Akira-san, is it?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aizawa Ruriko-san is your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your mother has been arrested for eating and drinking\Nwithout money at a restaurant in Ningyouchou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will you become her identity's guarantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What happens when there's no guarantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until the punishment is determined,\Nshe'll remained in detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can't I be instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are?\N{\3c&H573235&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be her guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it's too hard, it's okay to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:58.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, since I want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:11.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-saaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, ..sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:19.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom had no money,\Nso I had a free eating..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:23.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You see I was really hungry\Nand didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring me to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Says a 'dine and dash' woman\Nwho then clings to her daughter in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone who even sold her picture to gain money,\Nwhat a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:39.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Such an arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what's up with the 50 million? The 50 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:46.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what's up with "I'll get the money somehow,\Nso don't meet Akira anymore"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with that admirable begging attitude,\Nyou're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey Akira,\Nlet's leave this place quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and live the two of us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,like we used to,\Nit'll be fun, both of us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Until when are you going to continue with that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:11.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I only had you, mother, back then, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were always drunk when coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that, being a mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had no alternative, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Going at school where everyone had their food for lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:27.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and for many, many days, you didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was lonely, so, so lonely.\N{\3c&H573235&}I'm sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:36.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just keep silent and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And because you didn't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:47.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and there was no money,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,not even confetti,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I had no one to go for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:10:00.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was so hungry..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:05.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was so hungry,\Nthat I even finished the ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And when you finally came back, you brought a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:12.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and ask me to wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and said, it'd have been better not to have that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:24.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although I was expecting to be hug..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:29.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd have been happy just to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had no only else, but you mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:46.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I worked and worked and worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in the hope for you to say\N'you can stay with me'..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I loved to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because you said my dancing was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:11.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I could dance well, I though that would please mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:18.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Money was really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:24.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because if I had money,\Nmom would hug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,'You're a good child'\Nand she'd pat my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:36.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I could please the customers,\NI could please mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:43.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She would be proud of me and praised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:49.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I just loved to see mother's happy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:53.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For a long time,\NI continue living like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, now I want to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I became who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:21.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:32.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:37.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira.. No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:43.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nooo..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm the one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:49.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,who's giving you a hug.\N{\3c&H573235&}Noo..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom, you were also lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, I can get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:13.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you have to put up with a lot of things\Nbecause of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:22.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, from now on, you don't have\Nto endure that for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:25.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:29.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Every minute until now,\NI'll properly return them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:32.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:46.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Noo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't want..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:55.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:59.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't want! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I became a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That Ennoji guy had a breakdown\Nand told me to become his horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He was shouting while riding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:19.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He said, "Go for the top"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:23.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi,\Nwhat do you consider to be the cause for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:26.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?\N{\3c&H573235&}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The acquisition business didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:34.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In exchange for the Minister's son's surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there was a promise\Nto receive a large quantity of subsidiary aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But that ended once was leaked\Nthat this Minister was doing tax evasion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:43.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see,\Nthat's probably a shock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's something strange about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister of Communications, Ike,\Ncontact me directly by phone, and..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and he was concern about a dilemma.\N{\3c&H573235&}Ike-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The dilemma was the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,, And the director ended up in such a condition,\Nwe're also troubled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Does he have any other symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:06.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,His face moved in this way,\Nwhen he was in rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do something, Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I'm under house confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't just say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you laughing? About my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it, Hino?\N{\3c&H573235&}I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you laughing!\N{\3c&H573235&}Even with this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:27.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You stole Yumeno from me,\Nyou are also trying to steal the future of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:33.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because of you,\Nthe hospital acquisition business has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't have the power or authority to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you have a grudge against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you plotting, Hino-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:50.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, I\Ndon't want to become your horse..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Be careful with your language, Hino-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you come just once to my examination room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'm sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who you are now,\Nand who you've been until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,don't resemble the same degree of rationality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you carrying a big amount\Nof stress in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:11.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That stress it's because of you!\NBecause of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't you suggest something to Minister Ike, Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:17.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, our acquisition business\Nwouldn't have failed so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was 60 billion, 60 billion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You guys also have Hino's opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'm sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, the current you\Nis similar to the Emperor's new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, to say that,\Nit's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that no one around you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is giving you an honest opinion\Nabout your present condition..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:54.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino, do not describe the Naked Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everything is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister Ike betrayed me!\NHasumi also changed sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa is a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone's fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:09.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That sharp condition is not usual,\Nwhat kind of symptoms are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:18.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's an acute stress disorder,\Nthat's causing a mild confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And the medical treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:22.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It could be good if he could listen to me..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:31.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, has been somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,contributing with the hospital until now,\NProfessor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he shouldn't be fired, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:41.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you all relying on Hino..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to be loved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Professor, I'm here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,want to be loved by my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\Nthink in a sort of solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I leave it to you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:26.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, how did it go?\N{\3c&H573235&}Mm.. not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I we don't do something immediately\Nhis condition certainty..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:33.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not that! With Yumeno-san, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but come as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't by the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand, then, could you wait\Nfor about a hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That much time.. I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm on a verge of panic!\NCome quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see, then I'll go immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:03.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-san, take a deep breath\Nand please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:10.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, until soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:24.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because you told me to break it,\NI broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:28.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, it became this messy,\Nwhat on earth should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:30.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, calm down, Ike-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is this a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:45.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, it's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:49.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew that Ennoji had requested
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,exorbitant subsidies to the Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(427.2,141.8)\frz353.1}Soumei\NMedical Corporation under suspicion for acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\frz351.8\pos(531.2,340.2)}Press\NMinister\NIke\Nalso\Ninvolved..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:57.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, before that happened, the Minister\Nwas under suspicion for tax evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:02.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why, I decided to break\NEnnoji's chopstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was just drawing together two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do something\Nto violate the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why\Nare you this much scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be you because you took bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:24.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-san, are you hiding anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:37.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been doing the same?\NAbout Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:43.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to particularly hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you still insisting that it's just\Na doctor-patient relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About that..\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:54.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it for her sake?\Nor for your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:04.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is there an answer, or you don't want to answer?\Nwhich one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:10.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister..\N{\3c&H573235&}There are things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:15.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that is better if they remain unclear\Nin this society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:23.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, you are suffering now of the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,consequences of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fate of a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:32.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it the same as the psychiatrists'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:37.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you can explain it in the conference\Nwon't they understand you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:42.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-san, prepare your stomach for the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:54.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In times like this, if there is a secret people will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:04.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to win an opponent trust\Nno matter what kind of punishment you may receive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:07.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,on this occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:10.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,shouldn't you expose everything to the daily light?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:30.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:54.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:56.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:02.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've just remembered the day when mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:08.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When I returned that day\Nall the dishes were washed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:12.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought mom\Nwas trying really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then the phone rang
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:17.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I knew she had jumped\Nin front of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you forgive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:45.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I mean yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:52.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Regarding this deal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:55.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was absolutely not involved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:58.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a lie?..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:02.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that Minister Kusunoki\Nhas testified that you introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:05.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director Ennoji to the Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:09.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Certainly, I was the one who introduced them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:12.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, about the matter of the acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:15.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had no participation at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:17.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's also certain
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:21.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,information of a secret meeting you had\Nwith the Director at Yoshino restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:24.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Was it there where the money\Nwas delivered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.51,0:24:26.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:29.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We were just having a nice talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.53,0:24:32.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop telling irresponsible lies,\Ntalk with the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.54,0:24:36.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister, What are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:39.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NWhat are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.51,0:24:43.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:51.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:55.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Other than this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.06,0:24:58.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I do not have any secrets at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:25:00.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.52,0:25:06.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even after this, can't you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:10.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even after this, are you still going to torment me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.01,0:25:17.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Somehow I feel sorry for the Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.58,0:25:21.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, there goes my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.00,0:25:23.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's definitely not coming true now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:25.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If the Dir. is also involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.51,0:25:28.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he might not come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.03,0:25:31.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't say bad things about the Dir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.03,0:25:34.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if he did something bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.03,0:25:38.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he has been always\Nsupporting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.59,0:25:40.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.52,0:25:43.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Koyume?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.03,0:25:48.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.51,0:25:50.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.57,0:25:59.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.11,0:26:00.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.99,0:26:03.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have this strange twitching
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.52,0:26:14.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It looks good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.02,0:26:17.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. will you taste it?\NIs it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.56,0:26:18.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.49,0:26:22.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.01,0:26:26.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.\N{\3c&H573235&}Ah.. great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.02,0:26:28.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.00,0:26:31.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.51,0:26:34.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Yumechiyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.51,0:26:36.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.04,0:26:38.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.08,0:26:42.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have an earnest request to ask you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.53,0:26:54.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the Minister to remove his wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.01,0:26:56.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.02,0:26:59.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He said he wasn't hiding a secret\Nand remove it in front of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.52,0:27:01.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Haven't you watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.51,0:27:04.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.02,0:27:07.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are a terrible guy, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.01,0:27:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dir. why are you so obsessed\Nabout the acquisition of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.02,0:27:19.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to remove my wig too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.51,0:27:22.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't have that intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.01,0:27:28.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Soumei medical corporation is my father's hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.08,0:27:31.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Father? The Dir.'s father?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.03,0:27:33.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.00,0:27:36.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to buy it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.01,0:27:38.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:42.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you have any brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.51,0:27:46.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just one younger sister.\N{\3c&H573235&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.07,0:27:48.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have two older brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Both of them are doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.02,0:27:54.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.53,0:27:59.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think the Dir. is also excellent enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:02.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He never asked me to become his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.53,0:28:08.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't study enough\Nand couldn't enter medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.02,0:28:12.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.01,0:28:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..I was a person who didn't raise any expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.53,0:28:22.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,not when I married or when his grandson was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.04,0:28:27.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.11,0:28:31.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,when I divorced,\Nbut he didn't show up not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.53,0:28:36.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted a cheesy revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.52,0:28:41.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to buy my father's important thing,\Ndismantling it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.02,0:28:43.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and to put it on sale,\Nthat's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:50.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder why..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:52.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Regarding Yumeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:57.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi and even Miyagawa\Neveryone, have been influenced by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.51,0:29:02.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was dumbfounded,\NI'm not at all interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.03,0:29:04.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not at all sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:07.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.07,0:29:12.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everything ends up being robbed from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:16.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, there's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.53,0:29:24.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tell me, am I sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.53,0:29:29.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here I have a twitch,\Nit doesn't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.59,0:29:32.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it psychosomatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.51,0:29:39.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, surely\Nyou were working too hard alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.53,0:29:43.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've been, until now,\Nexchanging your sorrow and pain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:47.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with an energy of anger\Nto stay alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.04,0:29:52.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is a tremendous energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.09,0:29:55.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You could climb up to this place\Nbecause 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.03,0:29:58.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you had that energy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.03,0:30:02.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But the energy of anger is like a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.54,0:30:07.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to burn, it'll use\Nanything it can lay its hands on,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.04,0:30:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And then, unnoticed, this flame
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.56,0:30:13.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will burn your own self, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.03,0:30:18.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean I'm burning out?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.00,0:30:21.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ah I'm moved to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:27.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why, it's good,\Neven if you couldn't do the acquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.03,0:30:31.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm penniless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.06,0:30:34.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I had invested all my money\Nin that acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:38.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've nothing left but a twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.51,0:30:40.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.03,0:30:44.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think it's fine\Nnot to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.51,0:30:46.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.02,0:30:52.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director,\Nwhy are you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.52,0:30:59.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because I'd no other place to go.\NIsn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.03,0:31:03.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because it is in here, isn't it?\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.01,0:31:06.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The thing that is important to you, in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.05,0:31:14.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now what you need is to\Nask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.51,0:31:18.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's good to rely on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.01,0:31:23.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Human beings are not as bad as\Nyou consider, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.01,0:31:36.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.53,0:31:39.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something is in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.52,0:31:43.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.00,0:31:47.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey? Where did she go?\NYumechiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.02,0:31:50.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, just now, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.02,0:31:57.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You said if there is something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.53,0:32:01.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, it looks like it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:04.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.01,0:32:07.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, what could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.10,0:32:17.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.52,0:32:20.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.51,0:32:23.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the condition for you to return to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.52,0:32:32.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.04,0:32:35.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You want to entrust me Ennoji's treatment,\NI'm already fired, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.61,0:32:38.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's probably better if you do it.\N{\3c&H573235&}I'll ask your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.53,0:32:49.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you intending to stop being a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.02,0:32:53.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have you already decided that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.51,0:32:55.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.53,0:32:57.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.53,0:33:01.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess there's nothing left to say.\NJust go, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:04.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ennoji, and also Yumeno's mother,\NI'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.52,0:33:06.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.54,0:33:08.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.52,0:33:13.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the first time\Nyou open your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:19.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's something really special about Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.12,0:33:26.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother!\N{\3c&H573235&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:29.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you listen to our talk just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.51,0:33:32.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Talk? I don't want to hear your talk never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.51,0:33:35.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan! It's not that,\Nhe's also my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.52,0:33:37.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.02,0:33:39.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.02,0:33:42.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No wonder why you only say strange things!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.57,0:33:45.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just she said she had no place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.63,0:33:47.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I ask her to come and help me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.51,0:33:49.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It also serves as therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:52.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You too, listen\Ncarefully to Dr. Akari words,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.02,0:33:54.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and heal properly\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.03,0:33:56.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.00,0:34:00.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just leave quick, now it's my turn!\NWhat are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.51,0:34:03.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai.\N{\3c&H573235&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.06,0:34:06.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, don't imagine something strange.\NIt's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.01,0:34:11.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of Ruri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.52,0:34:14.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, just do what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.52,0:34:17.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.01,0:34:22.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.01,0:34:25.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've told you it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:27.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.02,0:34:36.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, it's going up here..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.03,0:34:37.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:40.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's my first time coming here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.04,0:35:11.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, it's my mother's 28th dead anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.05,0:35:14.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:16.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you said it's your first time..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.03,0:35:19.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did not come for 27 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.12,0:35:23.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.54,0:35:28.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell you this yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.03,0:35:36.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My father\Nworked overseas and he used to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:40.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,leave the house for long periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.06,0:35:46.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At that time, I think my mother was having\Nan affair with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.03,0:35:50.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was at high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.54,0:35:54.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I never had the courage to ask her\Nabout that, 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.04,0:36:00.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I never talked to her about it. Just in my heart,\NI blamed her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.05,0:36:05.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think my mom perceived that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.05,0:36:13.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That made her fall in depression\Nand drove her to suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.02,0:36:15.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.53,0:36:20.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I didn't forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.57,0:36:23.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and didn't allow myself to come here all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:34.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.05,0:36:52.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.55,0:36:56.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're able to come\Nand properly visit her grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.04,0:37:00.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.56,0:37:07.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In spite of being a psychiatrist, I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.06,0:37:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,being trying to escape from facing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.63,0:37:14.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is\NI was scared of facing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.54,0:37:21.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I cease to escape when I met with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.56,0:37:26.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because you filled\Nthe emptiness within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.09,0:37:33.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.14,0:37:38.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.03,0:37:42.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rather than as a healer,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.55,0:37:47.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I love you as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.05,0:37:55.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to spend my life\Nmaking you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.61,0:37:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.53,0:38:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.56,0:38:12.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's unexpected for a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.04,0:38:15.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I really wanted to convey
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.08,0:38:19.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my feelings towards you, here\Nin front of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.55,0:38:22.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since, I'm behaving so arbitrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.04,0:38:25.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you don't have to answer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.07,0:38:36.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I will answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.02,0:38:43.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.04,0:38:48.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.53,0:38:51.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,can't marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.55,0:38:58.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.09,0:39:00.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.53,0:39:07.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When a psychiatrist falls in love\Nwith his patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.55,0:39:10.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that's called Counter-transference, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.55,0:39:13.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.04,0:39:16.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was written in your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.56,0:39:23.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Love is like a temporal mental illness."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.03,0:39:26.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, my feelings for you, Akira-san are..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.53,0:39:31.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with the psychiatrist Hino Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.54,0:39:38.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And to hear those passionate words\Nof wanting to spend your life trying to make a patient happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.06,0:39:40.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that makes you untrustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.55,0:39:49.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.04,0:39:52.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To say such a terrible thing\Nabout your son, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.60,0:40:05.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.54,0:40:09.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a patient,\Ncould you answer me one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.53,0:40:11.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.55,0:40:15.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's about my illness,\Nhaven't I healed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.55,0:40:22.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I think\Nyou are a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.11,0:40:25.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, if something\Ntroubles you again
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.54,0:40:28.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please come for examination at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.05,0:40:32.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.04,0:40:39.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:41:08.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.64,0:41:10.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You got rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.56,0:41:12.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.54,0:41:14.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She was your patient, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.54,0:41:17.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So then, isn't that an ethical violation?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.03,0:41:22.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to marry her,\NI properly propose..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.05,0:41:25.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean she rejected your proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.59,0:41:27.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How many times will you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.04,0:41:33.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:36.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please prepare for Rintaro his favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.05,0:41:37.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.55,0:41:41.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I just.. remember something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:44.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait..Mizushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.07,0:41:48.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.63,0:41:53.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yuriko-san\Nhad to leave because of the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.55,0:41:55.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, speaking of that..
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.55,0:41:58.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There were beautiful lilies at the grave, so
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.55,0:42:02.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that was you, right, Madoka-chan?\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.54,0:42:04.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.56,0:42:06.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.53,0:42:09.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those were from Yuriko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.60,0:42:13.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She had been leaving flower offerings every anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.55,0:42:15.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.05,0:42:18.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Brother, how could you let such thing passed unnoticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.54,0:42:20.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why\Nyou got rejected even at this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.92,0:42:22.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, those are different..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:24.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't get a woman's heart at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.04,0:42:33.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.54,0:42:35.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.54,0:42:47.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.59,0:42:49.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sis Yumeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.62,0:42:51.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.54,0:42:53.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.05,0:43:09.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san,\Nare you really okay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.62,0:43:13.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You really like Rintaro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.04,0:43:17.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And if you, Dr. Mizushima\Ndidn't like Dr. Rintaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.03,0:43:20.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have specially come\Nto see me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.55,0:43:25.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've always been looking after Rintaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.52,0:43:27.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want him to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.59,0:43:32.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Besides me, Dr. Hino\Nhas a lot of patients
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.55,0:43:34.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that need to be saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.03,0:43:39.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think it's wrong to become the only one he helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.54,0:43:42.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.54,0:43:47.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Mizushima,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.08,0:43:52.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,about Dr. Hino,\Nplease take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.55,0:43:55.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.54,0:43:59.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I'm\Nfar from getting married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.04,0:44:03.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard as a geisha,\NI would like to repay the mother I have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.57,0:44:10.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.12,0:44:12.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We have to get ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.54,0:44:23.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, if you could leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.05,0:44:34.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.59,0:44:37.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you have any appetite?\N{\3c&H573235&}I have appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.53,0:44:40.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you sleep well?\N{\3c&H573235&}Almost all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.53,0:44:43.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Fukuhara-kun, why?\N{\3c&H573235&}When just been dumped
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.05,0:44:46.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,now, you might have a hole\Nin your heart, this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.05,0:44:47.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.56,0:44:52.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, Dr. Hino's favorite comedian\Nhas this saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:55.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"To equal things like love and finding happiness is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.11,0:44:57.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Happiness is a different thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.55,0:45:00.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When did I say that I got dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.03,0:45:02.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know it just by looking at you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.68,0:45:03.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.64,0:45:06.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't help patients with an examination\Nbased on guessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.54,0:45:09.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not a way of having empathy either.\N{\3c&H573235&}So..Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.06,0:45:14.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.10,0:45:16.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya-kun, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.55,0:45:22.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.06,0:45:29.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.55,0:45:31.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,got..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.05,0:45:33.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,dum-
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.55,0:45:35.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,ped!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.07,0:45:37.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.06,0:45:42.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., it's time for your lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:44.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.05,0:46:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(270.4,135.4)}Physician guidelines:\N\N\NEmpathy as the starting point
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.05,0:46:06.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalysis is the science of empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.54,0:46:11.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not all mental disorders are diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.52,0:46:15.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My conclusion is that it's has to do with the personality of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.04,0:46:21.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even without gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.03,0:46:23.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.05,0:46:29.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even without gambling..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.52,0:46:32.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry~
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.03,0:46:36.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A little longer, a bit more, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.58,0:46:40.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just another 100 times until noon break.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.54,0:46:44.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.06,0:46:55.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.53,0:46:57.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.07,0:47:01.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to eat tendon \N(fried fish served over a bowl of rice){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.02,0:47:05.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's not possible,\NI want to eat katsudon (pork cutlet on rice).
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.53,0:47:07.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's not possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.55,0:47:12.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at least I want bowl of rice with eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.55,0:47:15.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.04,0:47:17.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please~
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.59,0:47:20.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, what about unadon (bowl of eel and rice)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.14,0:47:22.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you~!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.54,0:47:25.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Being terrible wounded at heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.55,0:47:30.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,many people fell into a mental illness\Ndue to lack of affection,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.55,0:47:34.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for them, the treatment only consists\Non something like pharmaceuticals
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.54,0:47:36.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or changing their mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.56,0:47:41.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For those cases, if the physician gets closer\Nwith empathy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.15,0:47:44.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's not unusual that the patient's condition\Nstarts to get better
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.53,0:47:46.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.53,0:47:50.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.54,0:47:54.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, you look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.04,0:47:56.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.06,0:47:58.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.55,0:48:00.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.12,0:48:04.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.04,0:48:07.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.54,0:48:09.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Regarding the medical treatment of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.56,0:48:13.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is it enough to only improved\Nthe symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.54,0:48:18.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not only that, shouldn't it be our goal\Nalso to guide the patient
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.55,0:48:22.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to a happier life?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.09,0:48:26.54,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it to do whatever the therapist can\Nin order to diminish the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.54,0:48:29.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,, patient's loneliness and sorrow, even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.04,0:48:32.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to become an umbrella for rainy days,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.53,0:48:37.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a blanket to wrap in\Non days of thunder
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.03,0:48:41.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what is necessary for us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.57,0:48:46.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not only as a therapist,\Nbut as people who love,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.03,0:48:49.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For people who want to give happiness to others,\Nit's common to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:54.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It might be the most difficult challenge \Nin life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.56,0:49:00.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because love means to support the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.56,0:49:04.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Holding someone tight\Nonly to content your own heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.13,0:49:07.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,can be a painful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.55,0:49:10.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Some people say love is an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.55,0:49:13.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A couple in love, as well as a family in love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.04,0:49:15.04,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,don't share just beautiful times,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.04,0:49:18.56,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,there are also times when\Nit becomes really uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.56,0:49:23.08,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,It's the same for us, as psychiatrists\Neven while having doubts,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.08,0:49:26.08,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,we face the patient day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.52,0:49:31.54,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,But if there is no genuine love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.54,0:49:35.54,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,for the people we want to save,\Nwe can't do something so overambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.54,0:49:39.53,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,To heal those we want to save
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.53,0:49:43.58,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,there's no other choice but to love,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.58,0:49:48.52,Default 1 - Up,,0,0,0,,we should genuinely love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.52,0:49:53.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.03,0:49:56.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, what do you think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.03,0:50:01.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, let me hear your opinions\Nconcerning today's topic.
